content: Welcome to Issue Triage, here we sort out which issues are related to this project group and which should be better left alone for others.
Just got a PM from haraldh that he would like us to take over this issue https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/58520
I think that one is already on our project tracker but if it isn't I'll definitely add it and I'll add it to the agenda/action items
Harald is willing to come to our next meeting to discuss it
Did they want to have the action item assigned to them
And we can help manage and support the work on it
Hmm I think they wanted for us to review it and probably conclude what to do with it (no mentions of action items)
Yea, that's more or less what I meant
Action item as in "make it an official task that we will consistently follow up on during our meetings"
I guess that in that sense, yeah
